Blight
Discworld ritual help
Blight

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Blight - Makes a target more vulnerable to harm.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Blight is an offensive ritual, causing its victim to become weaker
and more susceptible to harm.  To perform this ritual you will
need the holy symbol of your god and a holy amulet.
.EP
